metadata.name: Convict Lake
metadata.description:
In the Sierra Nevada mountain range in California, Convict Lake is named for a group of convicts who escaped and had a shoot out with the sheriff.

Thankfully there was no such ruckus on the morning I was there. It was the most peaceful and calm sunrise with a perfectly still reflection on the lake.
